title: 'solution : use a "set" instead'
pid: 17266879-cd2b-47e2-aaf9-2f7893e45fac
body: |2-
  This way, scaling the data by 1,000
  scales performance time only slightly more than 1,000.

  (It doesn't actually help to represent the list of people as a set;
  you'll have to iterate through them either way.)
